  {
    "num": 5,
    "title": "臨床での実践",
    "style": "light",
    "content": "TSH中心の診断フロー",
    "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}body{font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:flex;flex-direction:column}.slide-light{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);color:#134e4a}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:20px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);color:#0d9488;font-size:15px;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px}.logo{font-size:15px;color:rgba(19,78,74,0.5)}.main{flex:1;display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 60px}.left-panel{flex:1}.section-label{font-size:15px;color:#0d9488;letter-spacing:4px;margin-bottom:16px}.section-title{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:30px;color:#134e4a}.list-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:20px}.list-num{min-width:48px;height:48px;background:#0d9488;color:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:26px;font-weight:700;margin-right:20px;flex-shrink:0}.list-text{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#334155;padding-top:8px}.list-sub{font-size:24px;color:#64748b;margin-top:4px}.footer{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:14px;opacity:0.4}</style><div class=\"slide slide-light\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">SLIDE 5/8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><div class=\"left-panel\"><div class=\"section-label\">結 ── 実践フロー</div><div class=\"section-title\">明日から使える診断ステップ</div><div class=\"list-item\"><div class=\"list-num\">1</div><div class=\"list-text\"><strong>まずTSHを測定</strong><div class=\"list-sub\">最も感度の高いスクリーニング検査</div></div></div><div class=\"list-item\"><div class=\"list-num\">2</div><div class=\"list-text\"><strong>TSH異常時 → FT4・FT3追加</strong><div class=\"list-sub\">顕性か潜在性かを判定</div></div></div><div class=\"list-item\"><div class=\"list-num\">3</div><div class=\"list-text\"><strong>病因検索</strong><div class=\"list-sub\">TSH低値 → TRAb（バセドウ病）<br>TSH高値 → TPO抗体・Tg抗体（橋本病）</div></div></div><div class=\"list-item\"><div class=\"list-num\">4</div><div class=\"list-text\"><strong>甲状腺エコーで形態評価</strong><div class=\"list-sub\">びまん性腫大・結節の有無を確認</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
