  {
    "num": 6,
    "title": "Take Home Message",
    "style": "accent",
    "content": "3つの持ち帰りポイント",
    "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}body{font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:flex;flex-direction:column}.slide-accent{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d4a4a,#14b8a6);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:20px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);color:#fff;font-size:15px;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px}.logo{font-size:15px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)}.main{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:0 60px}.section-title{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px}.thm-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);border-radius:20px;padding:28px 36px;margin-bottom:20px;display:flex;align-items:center;backdrop-filter:blur(10px)}.thm-num{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;color:#2dd4bf;min-width:60px}.thm-text{font-size:26px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.5;margin-left:16px}.footer{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:14px;opacity:0.6}</style><div class=\"slide slide-accent\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">SLIDE 6/8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><div class=\"section-title\">Take Home Message</div><div class=\"thm-card\"><div class=\"thm-num\">01</div><div class=\"thm-text\">不定愁訴・脂質異常・心房細動・CK上昇 → TSHを追加せよ</div></div><div class=\"thm-card\"><div class=\"thm-num\">02</div><div class=\"thm-text\">甲状腺触診を日常診察のルーチンに組み込む</div></div><div class=\"thm-card\"><div class=\"thm-num\">03</div><div class=\"thm-text\">潜在性異常でも抗体陽性なら定期フォロー（年間4.3%が顕性化）</div></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
